Title: Cashin (Bonnie) Collection of Fashion, Theater and Film Costume Design, 1913-2000
Description.abstract: The collection contains Bonnie Cashin's personal archive documenting her design career. The collection includes Cashin's design illustrations, writings on design, contractual paperwork, photographs of her clothing designs, and press materials including press releases and editorial coverage of her work. Personal photographs and letters to Cashin are also included.
